{"tid":2292943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"至少4度生擒野鴿恐作食用　長沙灣大叔：畀個老友","createTime":"2020-11-20T01:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T02:12:05.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4143d719ea55e3da05caaf28e3d6f9490304afb8","tid":2292943,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2806959/123123_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2806959%2F123123_1024.jpeg&h=1e72e1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港近來頻頻出現疑似活捉雀鳥事件，近日長沙灣一名大叔生疑生擒白鴿，有女途人見狀上前質問，大叔聲稱用來「畀老友」，並向港鐵站逃去。有關注組織表示，涉事大叔今年內已至少第4次被人發現圖捉白鴿，有人擔心他捉鴿目的是食用。<br />\n關注雀鳥保育的「香港救援鳩鴿及雀鳥」於Facebook專頁發帖，指本周二（17日）接獲市民舉報，目睹長沙灣有一名大叔於麗閣商場對出馬路捉白鴿。<br />\n從其上傳的影片中可見，一名戴著黑色鴨舌帽，身穿白色上衣的大叔，被女途人於港鐵站內追問為何要捉白鴿，並指擔心他食用白鴿，大叔則回應指：「我畀人，畀個老友」、「我而家放生㗎喇」。其後女子大喊：「如果我唔話你，你點會放生呀？」，大叔承認並表示不會「唔記得」。有見對方不斷窮追，大叔最終求饒道：「對唔住！唔好追住我，唔好意思呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2806959/230a9646-6e20-456d-a746-5bcd5474554d_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2806959%2F230a9646-6e20-456d-a746-5bcd5474554d_censored_600.jpg&h=24fd6f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大叔被追著質問時，跑入港鐵站。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n年內第4次被市民目擊捉白鴿<br />\n「香港救援鳩鴿及雀鳥」表示，今年已至少第4次接獲市民舉報該名大叔捉白鴿。而事發經過多為大叔被人發現打算捉鴿入袋，遭指責後便會放生，他又會解釋自己打算「捉嚟養」。該專頁指案發日期包括：<br />\n4月11日，金魚街街尾，萬寧斜對面；<br />\n7月21日，金魚街水渠道；<br />\n8月13日，金魚街街尾，萬寧斜對面；<br />\n11月17日，長沙灣麗閣商場對出馬路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2806959/7788b02f-e5f5-4556-8ad7-3b717405a19a_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2806959%2F7788b02f-e5f5-4556-8ad7-3b717405a19a_censored_600.jpg&h=bf868cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7月份大叔曾被人指控鬼祟捉鴿。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n隨街捉鴿恐犯法 最高囚1年<br />\n「香港救援鳩鴿及雀鳥」續指，近年虐鴿和捉鴿人士的行為越發猖狂，提醒大定遇到類似情況，應冷靜地拍攝整個過程，然後上前喝止，再報警處理。<br />\n根據香港法例第170章（野生動物保護條例），所有野生雀鳥均受法例保護，違例者最高刑罰為罰款10萬及監禁1年，未經許可管有或使用捕獸器亦屬違法，最高刑罰為罰款20萬及監禁3年。"},{"pid":"6876861711caaecebd165dc581a774cc65b21ba8","tid":2292943,"uid":73849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"正一死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597a4deca78f1680f2c1c1fa7d07ab0f45a3cdf2","tid":2292943,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"我係中国人啊Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64a521dc44ca00bad7b56023e9aaf3d78e7ee50","tid":2292943,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"打雀英雄傳"},{"pid":"91560045a41a59565bf2735c84f1e691f8adc004","tid":2292943,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:55:55.000Z","msg":"廢老個腦究竟咩構造"},{"pid":"75354b45aafde902d67d5a0a567df246c18334ea","tid":2292943,"uid":226248,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:58:33.000Z","msg":"D鴿就係信人類係安全先唔飛走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d267d47f40ee2eaacf3b8a6ba97f1884d828cb","tid":2292943,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"禽流感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e77b217ca0dc6bb30a0192ad2e62ae55cc28783","tid":2292943,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75354b45aafde902d67d5a0a567df246c18334ea","tid":2292943,"uid":226248,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:58:33.000Z","msg":"D鴿就係信人類係安全先唔飛走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"而麻雀一定唔會信人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff0ae89c67e36ecbe84c4556d9775644a6e5f8f","tid":2292943,"uid":35342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"不過嗰啲位真係好撚多鴿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲病毒俾廢老食咗兩個一齊死都係好事黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}